a131			; | | By default break points are off. Either the above can be used to enable them 
a131			; | | or if a key is held down during start up the spashscreen will appear to freeze 
a131			; | | and on release of the pressed key the CONFIG menu will be displayed where you 
a131			; | | can disable break points. Exiting will then continue boot process. 
